text: @SkyeWolfieits Yeah I enjoyed my time on twitter at first but its time to move on
Ima be on for today to let people know I'm dipping and we out.

As for where I'll be you can find on AOTY in the name RenIsNowNas and on some of my friends clips but that's it. I'm done with Social Media. Thank you for you're time and I'll catch you on the flipside. 💕
My Journey is over with twitter and I'm thankful I got to meet some of my best friends on this platform looking at you buddy @SkyeWolfieits. But I'm done posting here.
As for friends who wants to still talk to me I have a discord you can add me in. RenBecomesKOI!?#3764 .

I thought really long and hard about this decision and I think its the right thing to do. Will I ever come back probably not but who knows. It's the best decision for me right now and I'm done posting for now.

Reason #3

 I wanted to make this account an art account. But after a week or so I began to realize it was already too late. I don't have a care for twitter anymore so posting my art ain't going to do shit.

Reason #2 

 This kinda goes with #1 but I've been noticing I been very negative as a person because of Twitter. I don't wanna feel like that anymore and I'm done with that. I'm done feeling like trash.

Reason #1

Twitter is a toxic environment and I don't want know part of it anymore. I constantly feel I have to fight for my life over something stupid and I don't care enough to continue that. I don't wanna argue with stubborn people who can't handle opinions.
I have an announcement to make. I'll be leaving twitter for good. Read the thread on why.
